    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forehead Chip </strong>is a sci-fi <strong>pixel-art</strong> <strong>platformer</strong> set in the middle of Arca City, a fracturing utopia. You’ve joined the <strong>Implant Corps </strong>to restore order by capturing vile <strong>Holdouts</strong>. Capture the most and you win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/4bed930cccad240457884e6874fb10a6.webp?t=1771944568\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e24b655e630df285f770db6b423ada61.poster.avif?t=1771944568\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e24b655e630df285f770db6b423ada61.webm?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e24b655e630df285f770db6b423ada61.mp4?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s all about maintaining <i>order.</i> And it’s your job to capture Holdouts. So you need to know the drill:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage your supply</strong> of implant bullets in <strong>tactical combat</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t destroy your enemies - <strong>capture them</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield a variety of distinctively controlled <strong>weapons</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fuse your ammo </strong>by injecting<strong> logic</strong> <strong>capsules</strong> that affect their behaviour</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t forget to ask your <strong>Sergeant</strong> and <strong>Commander</strong> for tips</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/abdaa908eb06c8c89f064e4d2e6c8ea2.webp?t=1771944568\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/20fa0eb62197ad8b2ea4e59cf13fe3ce.poster.avif?t=1771944568\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/20fa0eb62197ad8b2ea4e59cf13fe3ce.webm?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/20fa0eb62197ad8b2ea4e59cf13fe3ce.mp4?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as young <strong>Chip</strong>, a recruit in the <strong>Implant Corps.</strong> Prove your worth to your friends and family by winning the coveted, <i>one-of-a-kind </i>implant: the <strong>Forehead Chip</strong>. Explore city locations, interact with characters across the societal divide, and pick your choices to determine the future of Arca City. Conquer and dominate... or is there another path? There are multiple endings to unlock and the Forehead Chip is up for grabs. Will you get it, or will someone else?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/f7a7d5cd4a4bb603b3e3977506738521.webp?t=1771944568\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/c46def5d6c89dd9f7a1d7ce2412b2773.poster.avif?t=1771944568\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/c46def5d6c89dd9f7a1d7ce2412b2773.webm?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/c46def5d6c89dd9f7a1d7ce2412b2773.mp4?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use skills, tactics, and trigger-conscious precision against enemies and obstacles:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight, tuned, responsive controls</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+</strong> types of enemies to fight and capture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four different <strong>districts</strong> to dropship into</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock</strong> new abilities and game modes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/541491b535de1a80a9f93b27d0c17c4c.webp?t=1771944568\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/d419b0a6d54a3211312c6374d497fdea.poster.avif?t=1771944568\" width=586 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/d419b0a6d54a3211312c6374d497fdea.webm?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/d419b0a6d54a3211312c6374d497fdea.mp4?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forehead Chip </strong>offers multiple gameplay modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single-player</strong> <strong>Campaign </strong>with various paths and endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture Holdouts side-by-side with <strong>2 Player Couch Co-op</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to <strong>4 Player PVP / Teams Multiplayer</strong> for laughs and yells with your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e19466c370add52cb2dca66893388b86.poster.avif?t=1771944568\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e19466c370add52cb2dca66893388b86.webm?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171910/extras/e19466c370add52cb2dca66893388b86.mp4?t=1771944568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUSIC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an awesome<strong> Retro Synthwave Soundtrack</strong> while you play with over 20+ tracks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTROLLER REQUIREMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad / SteamDeck recommended!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard+mouse are supported in single-player<i> </i>mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All multiplayer modes and arenas <i>require</i> a gamepad per player! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer keyboard and advanced custom controls can be set via config file.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100% HAND-CRAFTED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All code written, all art drawn, all dialog and everything else in the game was made without AI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to <strong>wishlist</strong> Forehead Chip on Steam!</p>",
